1
00:00:01,133 --> 00:00:02,567
<i>Nakipagrelasyon siya
bago siya umalis ng Maynila?</i>

2
00:00:02,667 --> 00:00:04,267
<i> Peter Montevilla.</i>

3
00:00:05,733 --> 00:00:07,400
<i> Hoy! Sino ka?!</i>

4
00:00:10,600 --> 00:00:11,900
<i> Sabihin mo sa akin kung bakit ka nandito,</i>

5
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:13,567
<i>o huhulihin kita
para sa trespassing!</i>

6
00:00:13,733 --> 00:00:14,867
<i>Kapatid mo!</i>

7
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:17,700
<i>Sa tingin ko may gagawin siya
bakit nawawala ang aking ama!</i>

8
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:18,733
<i> Ang kanyang pangalan ay Sandro Soliman!</i>

9
00:00:18,933 --> 00:00:20,767
<i>- Kailan siya nawala?
- Limang buwan na ang nakalipas.</i>

10
00:00:20,933 --> 00:00:22,267
<i> Sino si Sandro Soliman?</i>

11
00:00:22,433 --> 00:00:25,200
<i>Huwag na huwag mong babanggitin
na pangalan sa bahay na ito.</i>

12
00:00:25,300 --> 00:00:26,567
<i> Tapos na ang usapang ito.</i>

13
00:00:26,667 --> 00:00:27,600
<i> Lumabas ka!</i>

14
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:29,067
<i> Umalis ka!</i>

15
00:00:35,933 --> 00:00:40,133
[HINIT NG MGA IBONG]

16
00:00:40,267 --> 00:00:45,267
[WATER SPLASHING]

17
00:00:46,167 --> 00:00:47,467
[SARI SQUEALING] Ah!

18
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:50,167
Binabati kita!
Wala na ang sumpa!

19
00:00:50,333 --> 00:00:52,000
[BIGHT MUSIC PLAYING]

20
00:00:52,133 --> 00:00:54,567
[SARI GIGGLING]

21
00:00:54,700 --> 00:00:57,333
- Sinabi ba sa iyo ng iyong lolo?
- Hindi, alam ko lang.

22
00:00:57,500 --> 00:01:01,233
Naniniwala ako sa ritwal ng aking lolo
epektibo ang pinag-uusapan.

23
00:01:01,367 --> 00:01:03,500
Ang ritwal na ginawa mo?

24
00:01:03,633 --> 00:01:05,667
Ginawa ng mga kapitbahay ko
ang parehong bagay bago.

25
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:08,700
Magkaibigan ba silang dalawa
sino rin ang nagtangkang magbuhat ng sumpa?

26
00:01:08,867 --> 00:01:09,867
Oo.

27
00:01:10,300 --> 00:01:11,933
anong nangyari?

28
00:01:12,067 --> 00:01:15,700
Well, naging mag-asawa sila,
at kalaunan ay nagtali.

29
00:01:15,867 --> 00:01:17,500
At ngayon,
may lima silang anak!

30
00:01:17,633 --> 00:01:18,667
- Huh?!
- Ano?!

31
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:20,200
[MATINDING MUSIKA MATUTULOY]

32
00:01:20,367 --> 00:01:21,367
[TUMITI NG MALAMANG SI SARI]

33
00:01:21,500 --> 00:01:22,200
Oo!

34
00:01:22,367 --> 00:01:23,800
Hindi lang sila
palayasin ang malas,

35
00:01:23,900 --> 00:01:25,433
ngunit natagpuan din nila
isa't isa.

36
00:01:25,567 --> 00:01:30,433
["PAANO KUNG TAYO NA LANG"
NI ANGELA KEN NAGLALARO]

37
00:01:30,567 --> 00:01:31,367
Teka.

38
00:01:31,500 --> 00:01:33,100
Maghintay, maghintay, maghintay, maghintay, maghintay.

39
00:01:33,233 --> 00:01:35,500
Teka, paano kung?

40
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:36,800
[SARI SQUEALS]

41
00:01:36,967 --> 00:01:39,533
Paano kung kayong dalawa ang magkatuluyan
magkasama, katulad nila?

42
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:43,167
Bakit? Pwede naman diba?

43
00:01:43,267 --> 00:01:45,900
Magkaibigan kayo.
Isa pa, pareho kayong single.

44
00:01:46,067 --> 00:01:47,400
["PAANO KUNG TAYO NA LANG"
MAGPATULOY]

45
00:01:47,567 --> 00:01:48,733
Universe!

46
00:01:48,867 --> 00:01:52,333
Pinagsama-sama ba ang ritwal
ibang pares?

47
00:01:52,867 --> 00:01:53,733
[SARI GIGGLES]

48
00:01:53,900 --> 00:01:54,733
[TUMITI NG AWKWARD SI JADE]

49
00:01:54,867 --> 00:01:55,633
Halika, Sari.

50
00:01:55,767 --> 00:01:59,233
Ito ay malamang na isang...
case-by-case basis.

51
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:01,567
Hindi yata kami ni Kiko
pareho ang magiging kapalaran.

52
00:02:01,733 --> 00:02:02,900
Kalokohan yan, Sari.

53
00:02:03,067 --> 00:02:04,033
Y-Oo.

54
00:02:04,167 --> 00:02:06,033
Hindi banggitin,
inaalis ang malas

55
00:02:06,167 --> 00:02:07,667
ay kung ano ang talagang mahalaga.

56
00:02:07,767 --> 00:02:08,567
Shh!

57
00:02:08,700 --> 00:02:10,067
["PAANO KUNG TAYO NA LANG"
MAGPATULOY]

58
00:02:10,200 --> 00:02:11,367
Sir Kiko!

59
00:02:11,500 --> 00:02:13,867
Baka nasa paligid si Sir Martin
at naririnig kita!

60
00:02:14,700 --> 00:02:15,600
Okay, makinig ka.

61
00:02:15,767 --> 00:02:19,167
Ipangako mo sa akin, ang usapang ito
hindi nangyari.

62
00:02:19,300 --> 00:02:20,600
Okay, bye-bye!

63
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:33,333
- Aray.
- Ay, sorry.

64
00:02:33,467 --> 00:02:34,767
[Tumawa ng mahina]
Mag-ingat ka.

65
00:02:35,133 --> 00:02:42,200
[TEMA MUSIC PLAYING]

66
00:03:34,967 --> 00:03:36,233
[MONETTE] Kumusta, Gio.

67
00:03:36,367 --> 00:03:39,800
[HINIT NG MGA IBONG]

68
00:03:48,033 --> 00:03:49,400
[MONETTE] Ngayon, tingnan ko.

69
00:03:51,033 --> 00:03:52,267
[KIKO] Kain na tayo?

70
00:03:53,367 --> 00:03:55,333
- Nagugutom ka ba?
- [JADE] Medyo.

71
00:03:55,533 --> 00:03:57,200
-Nasaan ang--
- Monette.

72
00:03:57,333 --> 00:03:59,467
Tungkol sa panauhin
na nagdulot ng kaguluhan...

73
00:04:00,067 --> 00:04:01,267
Tungkol kay Chase.

74
00:04:05,500 --> 00:04:07,433
[GIO]
Nasa amin pa ang mga gamit niya.

75
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,867
Hindi ba dapat natin itong ibalik
sa lokal na town hall?

76
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:12,033
Hindi ngayon.

77
00:04:12,567 --> 00:04:14,467
Siya pa rin ang bisita namin.

78
00:04:17,033 --> 00:04:19,467
Kapag matino na siya, sa tingin mo
pwede mo ba siyang makausap?

79
00:04:19,567 --> 00:04:20,767
[MONETTE] Gumamit lang ng saging.

80
00:04:21,333 --> 00:04:22,600
Sa tingin ko ay hindi na kailangan iyon.

81
00:04:23,533 --> 00:04:25,600
Mas malaki ang problema natin.

82
00:04:26,167 --> 00:04:27,100
[LUMINISIN NI JUSTIN]

83
00:04:27,767 --> 00:04:29,167
Ang bangko ay may
nagpadala na ng notice

84
00:04:29,267 --> 00:04:30,667
tungkol sa utang ng hotel.

85
00:04:34,067 --> 00:04:35,033
Luna.

86
00:04:35,567 --> 00:04:37,067
[GLOOMY MUSIC PLAYING]

87
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,667
[JUSTIN]
Luna, kailangan nating mag-usap.

88
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:54,567
[MAGPAPATULOY ANG MAKULAMANG MUSIKA]

89
00:04:54,700 --> 00:04:56,033
- Monette.
- [MONETTE] Oh?

90
00:04:56,867 --> 00:04:58,567
Ayos ba yung dalawa?

91
00:04:59,933 --> 00:05:02,133
Parang nag-uusap sila
tungkol sa kaguluhan kagabi.

92
00:05:02,300 --> 00:05:04,100
Nag away sila?

93
00:05:04,267 --> 00:05:05,600
Hindi.

94
00:05:05,733 --> 00:05:07,933
Tungkol ito sa kaibigan ni Luna na
nagche-check in sa amin ngayon.

95
00:05:08,100 --> 00:05:10,067
Nalasing siya at naging maingay.

96
00:05:10,933 --> 00:05:12,433
kaibigan?

97
00:05:12,967 --> 00:05:16,167
Maghintay, hindi ko akalain na siya
nabanggit ang isang kaibigan na ganoon.

98
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:19,267
Well, hindi ako magtataka
kung hindi mo siya kilala.

99
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:22,267
Yung mga sinasabi niya
tungkol kay Luna...

100
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:25,033
Pati si Justin nahuli
sa kaguluhan.

101
00:05:25,133 --> 00:05:26,400
[MAGPAPATULOY ANG MAKULAMANG MUSIKA]

102
00:05:26,533 --> 00:05:27,933
Maraming bagay
nangyari na

103
00:05:28,100 --> 00:05:29,533
nung wala kami.

104
00:05:30,467 --> 00:05:32,867
Hindi na kailangang sabihin, mayroon sila
marami sa kanilang plato.

105
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,300
[JUSTIN]
Luna, kailangan nating mag-usap.

106
00:05:36,467 --> 00:05:37,933
para saan?

107
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:40,300
Kaya maaari mong paalalahanan ako
ang gulo ng buhay ko?

108
00:05:40,467 --> 00:05:41,700
Hindi, Luna.

109
00:05:41,833 --> 00:05:44,100
-Natutunan ko ang tungkol sa--
- Hindi salamat, Justin.

110
00:05:44,233 --> 00:05:45,967
Okay na ako sa narinig ko.

111
00:05:47,167 --> 00:05:48,367
Napansin.

112
00:05:49,733 --> 00:05:51,467
nga pala,
hindi ka ba suspended?

113
00:05:51,633 --> 00:05:52,933
bakit ka nandito?

114
00:05:53,967 --> 00:06:00,800
[SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING]

115
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,633
Tsk.

116
00:06:10,367 --> 00:06:12,133
May malaking problema tayo.

117
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:14,833
Nasa likod kami
sa pagbabayad.

118
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,000
[MOROSE MUSIC PLAYING]

119
00:06:16,133 --> 00:06:17,433
Dalawang buwan na late.

120
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:25,133
Posible bang mag-apela
para sa extension?

121
00:06:25,267 --> 00:06:26,600
yun lang
isang extension, Martin.

122
00:06:26,700 --> 00:06:29,000
Kailangan pa nating humanap ng paraan
para mabayaran sila.

123
00:06:29,133 --> 00:06:30,000
[LEON] Sa ngayon,

124
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:32,733
pera lang ang pumapasok
mula sa mga operasyon ng hotel.

125
00:06:32,867 --> 00:06:34,767
Ngunit ang pagdiriwang ng musika ay nagdala
sa magandang kita, tama ba?

126
00:06:34,867 --> 00:06:37,433
Oo, ngunit nagkaroon kami
para magbigay ng mga diskwento

127
00:06:37,533 --> 00:06:39,633
sa lahat ng abala
sa pamamagitan ng patay na daga.

128
00:06:39,767 --> 00:06:42,000
At pagkatapos ng kabiguan
kinasasangkutan ni Chase at Justin.

129
00:06:42,667 --> 00:06:44,800
Nag-usap na kami
kay Justin.

130
00:06:44,900 --> 00:06:47,700
Pansamantala siyang nasuspinde
mula sa mga tungkulin sa hotel.

131
00:06:47,867 --> 00:06:50,200
Ngunit iyon lamang ay hindi malulutas
ang problema natin.

132
00:06:51,300 --> 00:06:52,767
[LEON] Kaya kailangan natin ng mga aktibidad

133
00:06:52,900 --> 00:06:54,300
- na mababa ang halaga,
- [PHONE CHIMES]

134
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:55,700
ngunit may mataas na pagbabalik.

135
00:06:56,333 --> 00:06:58,467
Mga promo na mangunguna
sa mga booking.

136
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:03,167
Kahit sino ay may mga ideyang makakatulong
kumita ng pera ang hotel?

137
00:07:03,733 --> 00:07:05,600
Lahat ng mga mungkahi ay malugod na tinatanggap.

138
00:07:05,733 --> 00:07:07,667
[MARTIN]<i> Tiyo, mayroon ka
</i> basahin ang panukala?

139
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,867
[MOROSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

140
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,200
<i> May deal ba tayo?</i>

141
00:07:11,333 --> 00:07:14,367
[LEON] Gayunpaman, kailangan nating mag-usap
bago natin ito ituloy.

142
00:07:15,100 --> 00:07:18,067
Oo. Kami na ang magdedesisyon
magkasama bilang isang pangkat.

143
00:07:22,233 --> 00:07:23,133
Martin?

144
00:07:23,267 --> 00:07:24,400
ha? Oo.

145
00:07:24,533 --> 00:07:26,333
Sige, aakyat na ako
may kasama.

146
00:07:26,433 --> 00:07:33,533
[MOROSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

147
00:07:34,067 --> 00:07:34,900
[PHONE CHIMES]

148
00:07:35,067 --> 00:07:36,900
[RONALD]<i>Magkita tayong muli.
</i> Dalhin mo si Sari.

149
00:07:41,767 --> 00:07:44,333
Sir, interesado talaga ako
sa bar mo.

150
00:07:44,333 --> 00:07:46,367
At mula nang makita ko ito,

151
00:07:46,367 --> 00:07:48,333
wow nakita ko agad
potensyal nito.

152
00:07:48,367 --> 00:07:49,767
[SCOFFS] Totoo naman.

153
00:07:50,133 --> 00:07:51,733
Masama lang ang pakiramdam ko na pinakawalan ito.

154
00:07:51,733 --> 00:07:53,367
Ngunit unahin ang pamilya.

155
00:07:54,100 --> 00:07:55,933
Kailangan ko na rin lumipat
papuntang America.

156
00:07:55,933 --> 00:07:57,200
understandable naman yun.

157
00:07:57,200 --> 00:07:59,767
Kaya siguro pwede tayong mag-usap
tungkol sa kontrata...

158
00:07:59,767 --> 00:08:01,133
[JUSTIN]
Sa tingin ba nila malulungkot ako

159
00:08:01,133 --> 00:08:02,300
tungkol sa pagiging suspendido?

160
00:08:02,300 --> 00:08:04,267
hindi ko man lang ginusto
na naroon pa rin.

161
00:08:04,267 --> 00:08:06,267
Oh, sandali, bro.
Oo, oo.

162
00:08:06,267 --> 00:08:07,400
[TELEPONO BEEP]

163
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:09,200
- Bro, kamusta ka na?
- Bro.

164
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:11,267
- Saan ka nanggaling?
- Mula sa hotel.

165
00:08:11,267 --> 00:08:13,767
- Anyway, ito si Trixie.
- Kilala ko siya.

166
00:08:13,767 --> 00:08:14,900
Oh?

167
00:08:16,633 --> 00:08:18,267
Ah, siya pala
pinag-uusapan mo...

168
00:08:18,267 --> 00:08:19,700
Mhm, siya yun.

169
00:08:19,700 --> 00:08:22,867
[MALAMANG NA MUSIC PLAYING]

170
00:08:22,900 --> 00:08:24,467
Ano ang sinabi niya? Anong--

171
00:08:24,467 --> 00:08:25,933
mauuna na ako bro.

172
00:08:26,300 --> 00:08:28,233
- Inom tayo mamaya.
- Sige.

173
00:08:28,900 --> 00:08:29,933
Justin.

174
00:08:31,967 --> 00:08:33,167
Justin, teka--

175
00:08:33,167 --> 00:08:36,767
[MALAMANG NA MUSIC PLAYING]

176
00:08:37,767 --> 00:08:39,367
Ano ang sinabi niya tungkol sa akin?

177
00:08:46,300 --> 00:08:47,767
[HUMINGIN] Sir!

178
00:08:48,067 --> 00:08:50,033
Ito ay higit pa sa aking araw-araw na sahod!

179
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:51,900
ayaw mo?

180
00:08:52,733 --> 00:08:53,867
Salamat po sir.

181
00:08:54,300 --> 00:08:55,467
maraming salamat po.

182
00:08:56,167 --> 00:08:57,467
Sir, may gusto po ba kayo?

183
00:08:57,467 --> 00:08:58,800
Pwede kitang ipagtimpla ng kape.

184
00:08:59,300 --> 00:09:01,100
O tanghalian? Ang treat ko.

185
00:09:01,500 --> 00:09:04,033
Binigyan ako ng boss ko ng insentibo.

186
00:09:04,033 --> 00:09:05,300
You know what, itago mo lang yan.

187
00:09:05,867 --> 00:09:08,300
Maghanda para sa susunod nating pagkikita
kasama si Tiyo Ronald.

188
00:09:08,533 --> 00:09:10,133
May meeting pa tayo?

189
00:09:10,133 --> 00:09:11,433
Shh! Ay--

190
00:09:11,967 --> 00:09:13,433
Sari, anong sinabi ko sayo?

191
00:09:14,867 --> 00:09:17,000
[BULONG]
May meeting pa tayo?

192
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,167
Oo.

193
00:09:18,167 --> 00:09:19,333
At darating ka.

194
00:09:19,333 --> 00:09:22,800
[QUIRKY MUSIC PLAYING]

195
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:25,333
Ano ang ibig mong sabihin
nagbago ang isip mo?

196
00:09:25,333 --> 00:09:27,433
Malapit na kami sa isang sale.

197
00:09:27,433 --> 00:09:28,767
- Sir?
- Paumanhin.

198
00:09:29,367 --> 00:09:31,267
Ibibigay ko na lang yata
sa ibang tao.

199
00:09:32,067 --> 00:09:34,300
Ano ba talaga ang ginawa ni Justin
sabihin sayo?

200
00:09:35,167 --> 00:09:36,867
Kaya ba nagbago ka
iyong isip?

201
00:09:37,367 --> 00:09:40,267
Actually, mabait naman si Justin.

202
00:09:40,733 --> 00:09:42,300
Malaki ang naitulong niya sa akin.

203
00:09:43,467 --> 00:09:45,100
Yung lalaking yun? talaga?

204
00:09:45,533 --> 00:09:47,700
Hindi naman halata pero oo.

205
00:09:48,733 --> 00:09:50,967
First time lang talaga
humingi siya ng favor sa akin.

206
00:09:52,367 --> 00:09:55,167
Isang pabor laban sa akin.
tama ba ako?

207
00:09:55,867 --> 00:09:57,167
[SIGHS] Hindi naman.

208
00:09:58,867 --> 00:10:00,833
Tiwala lang ako sa judgement ni Justin.

209
00:10:01,267 --> 00:10:04,033
Kung sasabihin niyang okay lang
para ibenta ito sa iyo,

210
00:10:04,033 --> 00:10:05,333
tapos ibibigay ko sayo.

211
00:10:07,233 --> 00:10:09,867
So ibig sabihin meron ako
para kumbinsihin siya?

212
00:10:10,400 --> 00:10:11,400
Oo.

213
00:10:12,067 --> 00:10:13,467
Mabait si Justin.

214
00:10:14,533 --> 00:10:16,733
Hindi ka mahihirapan.

215
00:10:19,867 --> 00:10:22,067
Sige mga bata,
ituloy mo lang ang pagkain, okay?

216
00:10:22,067 --> 00:10:23,533
- [GIGGLES]
- Okay.

217
00:10:23,533 --> 00:10:25,133
Salamat, Miss Jade.

218
00:10:25,767 --> 00:10:28,033
Naku, huwag kang magpasalamat sa akin.

219
00:10:28,033 --> 00:10:30,533
Salamat Sir Edward.
Siya ang nagbigay niyan.

220
00:10:30,533 --> 00:10:33,300
- Salamat, Sir Edward.
- Salamat, Sir Edward.

221
00:10:34,867 --> 00:10:36,433
- Kumain ka na lang, okay?
- Ituloy mo lang ang pagkain.

222
00:10:36,433 --> 00:10:37,567
salamat po.

223
00:10:38,933 --> 00:10:40,100
Edward, pork buns?

224
00:10:41,800 --> 00:10:42,833
salamat po.

225
00:10:44,100 --> 00:10:45,533
Salamat sa lunch date.

226
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:48,900
Wow.

227
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:52,100
Iyon ang unang pagkakataon
nagpasalamat ka sa akin.

228
00:10:52,900 --> 00:10:55,400
[MALAMANG NA MUSIC PLAYING]

229
00:10:55,967 --> 00:10:59,867
Alam mo, sa lahat
mga lunch date natin,

230
00:11:00,267 --> 00:11:01,833
ito ang paborito ko.

231
00:11:04,467 --> 00:11:06,433
Hindi lang ako yung
gusto mong makipag-date.

232
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,200
ano yun?

233
00:11:12,133 --> 00:11:13,967
wala. Sabi ko hayaan na lang natin
tapusin ang aming tanghalian.

234
00:11:13,967 --> 00:11:17,300
[MAGPATULOY ANG SOFT MUSIC]

235
00:11:18,233 --> 00:11:19,433
Edward, okay ka lang?

236
00:11:20,500 --> 00:11:22,233
May... may mali ba?

237
00:11:26,233 --> 00:11:27,367
Naiintindihan ko.

238
00:11:28,067 --> 00:11:30,067
So hindi ka talaga pupunta
para ibahagi, ha?

239
00:11:33,167 --> 00:11:34,433
Diba sabi mo...

240
00:11:35,967 --> 00:11:38,033
...share lang kami
ano ang gusto nating ibahagi?

241
00:11:39,933 --> 00:11:41,533
Walang pilitan diba?

242
00:11:42,433 --> 00:11:49,333
[MAGPATULOY ANG SOFT MUSIC]

243
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,300
Kumusta ang mga bagay sa hotel?

244
00:12:06,467 --> 00:12:07,567
Aba...

245
00:12:08,267 --> 00:12:09,900
...maraming bagay
hindi naging maganda.

246
00:12:12,967 --> 00:12:13,967
Parang?

247
00:12:15,300 --> 00:12:16,333
Aba...

248
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:18,600
...isang bisita ang nagdulot ng eksena.

249
00:12:19,333 --> 00:12:21,400
Ngunit ang mas malaking problema
ay ang bank notice.

250
00:12:21,400 --> 00:12:24,267
Ngunit huwag mag-alala tungkol doon.

251
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:27,000
Kami na ang bahala. ayos lang.

252
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,367
Kamusta ang leave mo?

253
00:12:31,367 --> 00:12:35,467
[SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING]

254
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,333
ayos lang.

255
00:12:40,133 --> 00:12:42,167
Nagawa ko
ang kailangan kong gawin.

256
00:12:43,233 --> 00:12:48,133
[MAGPAPATULOY ANG SOMBRE MUSIC]

257
00:12:48,500 --> 00:12:49,567
Sige.

258
00:12:49,567 --> 00:12:52,033
Tapusin na natin itong lunch date.

259
00:12:52,033 --> 00:12:53,333
Baka may magalit.

260
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:55,367
ha?

261
00:12:55,367 --> 00:12:56,700
[SCOFFS] Sino?

262
00:12:58,567 --> 00:13:00,000
Paano ko malalaman?

263
00:13:01,067 --> 00:13:03,100
Sinong magagalit?
Mga kapatid ko?

264
00:13:03,100 --> 00:13:04,433
Bakit sila magagalit?

265
00:13:04,433 --> 00:13:06,300
- Nakakatawa ka.
- Hindi sila.

266
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,700
Iba ang pinag-uusapan ko.

267
00:13:10,567 --> 00:13:12,300
Parang boyfriend?

268
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,300
Yun ba ang ibig mong sabihin?

269
00:13:16,167 --> 00:13:18,000
[BOY] Oh, tingnan mo, isang lobo!

270
00:13:19,367 --> 00:13:20,400
Halika na!

271
00:13:23,267 --> 00:13:24,333
Takbo!

272
00:13:25,700 --> 00:13:27,200
Tara na!

273
00:13:27,400 --> 00:13:34,367
["PAANO KUNG TAYO NA LANG?"
NI ANGELA KEN NAGLALARO]

274
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:35,700
[LINISIN ANG LUMAIN]

275
00:13:36,233 --> 00:13:38,600
Hello, mga kaibigan. Ang pangalan ko ay Kiko.

276
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:40,600
Kiko, para sa atin ba ito?

277
00:13:41,100 --> 00:13:42,667
Walang kaarawan.

278
00:13:43,100 --> 00:13:45,200
[KIKO] Ay mga lobo
para lang sa kaarawan?

279
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:46,733
Oo.

280
00:13:46,733 --> 00:13:48,633
Sige, magpanggap na lang tayo
kaarawan mo.

281
00:13:48,633 --> 00:13:50,133
Maligayang kaarawan!

282
00:13:50,133 --> 00:13:52,633
- Salamat!
- Salamat!

283
00:13:52,633 --> 00:13:53,533
Halika na.

284
00:13:53,733 --> 00:13:54,733
Tara na.

285
00:13:57,300 --> 00:13:58,433
Laro tayo!

286
00:14:01,433 --> 00:14:02,467
Bigyan mo ako ng asul!

287
00:14:02,467 --> 00:14:09,600
["PAANO KUNG TAYO NA LANG?"
PATULOY SA PAGLALARO]

288
00:14:16,467 --> 00:14:18,600
Kaya ikaw
kaya interesado dito.

289
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:20,267
Sobrang saya ng mga bata
para makasama.

290
00:14:21,767 --> 00:14:24,567
Pero, bakit ka nandito?

291
00:14:26,900 --> 00:14:29,067
Ayoko ng multo.

292
00:14:29,100 --> 00:14:30,633
[MALAMANG NA MUSIC PLAYING]

293
00:14:30,633 --> 00:14:33,833
multo? saan? may multo ba?
Anong multo?

294
00:14:33,833 --> 00:14:35,933
Hindi, Jade...

295
00:14:35,933 --> 00:14:37,733
May sasabihin ako sayo.

296
00:14:38,700 --> 00:14:39,900
ano yun?

297
00:14:41,700 --> 00:14:42,767
Kasi, Jade...

298
00:14:42,767 --> 00:14:44,000
[BATA] Tita Jade!

299
00:14:44,767 --> 00:14:46,600
Oh. [TUMITIW]

300
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:48,033
Wow!

301
00:14:48,033 --> 00:14:49,933
Wow, ginawa mo ito?

302
00:14:49,933 --> 00:14:51,700
Ano ito?

303
00:14:51,700 --> 00:14:53,467
[BATA] Ikaw pala yan
at tito Kiko!

304
00:14:53,467 --> 00:14:55,600
[MAGPATULOY ANG SOFT MUSIC]

305
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:56,767
Ah.

306
00:14:57,667 --> 00:14:59,533
- Kami yan?
- [ANAK] Oo!

307
00:14:59,533 --> 00:15:01,967
Ikaw at ang iyong
ang ganda ng boyfriend.

308
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:06,033
Boyfriend? Ay naku.
[NAKAKATAWANG TUMITI]

309
00:15:06,033 --> 00:15:09,233
Alam mo, ang iyong drawing ay
maganda, pero...

310
00:15:09,233 --> 00:15:12,667
hindi kami nagde-date!

311
00:15:12,667 --> 00:15:16,133
Hindi ko siya... boyfriend!
[NAKAKATAWANG TUMITI]

312
00:15:16,133 --> 00:15:19,500
[BATA] Hindi mo siya boyfriend?
Tapos ano siya sayo?

313
00:15:19,500 --> 00:15:23,000
[MAGPATULOY ANG SOFT MUSIC]

314
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:25,700
Um... well...

315
00:15:25,700 --> 00:15:27,133
matalik na kaibigan!

316
00:15:27,133 --> 00:15:29,167
Bestfriend kami ni Kiko!

317
00:15:29,167 --> 00:15:31,267
[BATA] Talaga, Tiyo Kiko?

318
00:15:33,967 --> 00:15:35,933
ha? [NAKAKATAWANG TUMITI]

319
00:15:36,667 --> 00:15:37,833
Oo..

320
00:15:38,733 --> 00:15:41,067
Mhm-hmm.
Magkaibigan kami ni Jade.

321
00:15:43,233 --> 00:15:46,000
Mhm-hmm. [TUMITIW]

322
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:52,900
[MAGPATULOY ANG SOFT MUSIC]

323
00:15:55,667 --> 00:15:59,533
Hey, Cheska. Halika, pakiusap.
Kailangan mong makausap si Justin.

324
00:15:59,533 --> 00:16:01,233
Bakit kailangan ko pa siyang kausapin?

325
00:16:01,233 --> 00:16:03,600
Ah, pakiusap, pakiusap, pakiusap,
please, please, please.

326
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:05,233
Maganda, pakiusap...

327
00:16:07,267 --> 00:16:09,100
May ginawa ka, di ba?

328
00:16:09,133 --> 00:16:10,900
wala.

329
00:16:10,900 --> 00:16:12,967
May ginawa ka.
anong ginawa mo

330
00:16:12,967 --> 00:16:14,767
wala!

331
00:16:14,767 --> 00:16:17,533
Alam mo kung ano?
Kilala kita, nagsisinungaling ka.

332
00:16:18,900 --> 00:16:21,833
Ikaw ay isang malakas na independyente
babae.

333
00:16:22,300 --> 00:16:26,867
Maaari mo siyang kausapin noon,
pero bakit hindi mo magawa ngayon?

334
00:16:26,867 --> 00:16:28,000
anong mali?

335
00:16:29,733 --> 00:16:32,267
Eh kasi...

336
00:16:32,267 --> 00:16:34,033
Dahil?

337
00:16:34,033 --> 00:16:36,200
Dahil may sinabi ako sa kanya.

338
00:16:36,200 --> 00:16:37,900
Like what exactly?

339
00:16:39,133 --> 00:16:40,900
May sinabi akong masama sa kanya.

340
00:16:42,067 --> 00:16:43,700
Parang ano?

341
00:16:44,767 --> 00:16:46,133
Aba...

342
00:16:46,133 --> 00:16:49,133
kahit ano!
may sinabi ako sa kanya.

343
00:16:49,133 --> 00:16:50,967
Ano ito?

344
00:16:50,967 --> 00:16:54,067
Masamang bagay, Cheska!

345
00:16:54,067 --> 00:16:56,067
Mga masasakit na salita.

346
00:16:57,233 --> 00:16:58,967
Nasaktan ko ang damdamin niya.

347
00:17:00,267 --> 00:17:02,200
Ah!

348
00:17:02,333 --> 00:17:07,100
Kaya pala pareho kayong nag-off
nung kasama namin si Maria!

349
00:17:07,833 --> 00:17:10,633
alam ko na! kaya lang
hindi ka niya ginugulo!

350
00:17:10,633 --> 00:17:13,700
Oo, oo.
Huwag kuskusin ito.

351
00:17:15,267 --> 00:17:17,433
Bakit kailangan ko siyang kausapin?

352
00:17:17,433 --> 00:17:20,400
Hay, hey, hey.
Halika, halika!

353
00:17:20,500 --> 00:17:22,800
Kausapin mo siya, please?

354
00:17:22,867 --> 00:17:27,100
Ito ay magiging mas madali para sa pareho
sa iyo, kung humihingi ka ng tawad.

355
00:17:27,333 --> 00:17:28,667
[SIGHS] Sorry?

356
00:17:28,800 --> 00:17:32,233
Bakit kailangan kong humingi ng tawad? Kung
hindi niya kinausap ang may-ari ng bar,

357
00:17:32,467 --> 00:17:35,067
Hindi sana ako nagkaroon ng ganitong problema
sa unang lugar.

358
00:17:37,100 --> 00:17:38,433
ha?

359
00:17:38,433 --> 00:17:41,800
Pareho kayong magulo. ikaw ay
parehong matanda, ayusin mo ang sarili mo.

360
00:17:41,800 --> 00:17:43,267
Hihingi ka lang ng tawad.

361
00:17:43,267 --> 00:17:44,600
Hay naku.

362
00:17:45,700 --> 00:17:48,733
Mabuti, mabuti, okay, mabuti.
hihingi ako ng tawad.

363
00:17:49,867 --> 00:17:50,833
Kahit ano.

364
00:17:51,967 --> 00:17:53,800
Kung may bar...

365
00:17:53,800 --> 00:17:55,133
kung nandoon ang bar...

366
00:17:56,167 --> 00:17:58,167
ikaw ang magiging manager, okay?

367
00:17:58,167 --> 00:18:00,300
[MELLOW MUSIC PLAYING]

368
00:18:00,300 --> 00:18:02,800
[SCOFFS] Manager.

369
00:18:02,800 --> 00:18:04,200
totoo naman!

370
00:18:05,033 --> 00:18:08,033
Ayaw mong maniwala sa akin?
Ibigay mo sa akin yan.

371
00:18:08,900 --> 00:18:11,400
Kung dumating ang bar
at ikaw ang magiging manager,

372
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:15,133
hindi mo kailangang gumawa ng mga trabaho
ganito na.

373
00:18:15,133 --> 00:18:16,800
ayaw mo ba nun?

374
00:18:16,800 --> 00:18:20,133
Hindi ako magiging manager,
kung hindi mo pagmamay-ari ang bar.

375
00:18:20,133 --> 00:18:22,333
Kailangan mong bilhin ito.

376
00:18:22,367 --> 00:18:25,333
Iyon ang punto.

377
00:18:25,533 --> 00:18:28,500
Kailangan mong kumbinsihin si Justin.

378
00:18:28,500 --> 00:18:29,900
Halika na.

379
00:18:30,367 --> 00:18:32,833
- Pag-iisipan ko.
- Huwag mo nang isipin ito.

380
00:18:32,833 --> 00:18:35,933
- Halika.
- Kailangan kong pag-isipan ito.

381
00:18:35,933 --> 00:18:37,367
Tsk.

382
00:18:37,700 --> 00:18:40,067
Okay, okay. gagawin ko.

383
00:18:40,067 --> 00:18:41,333
- Iyan ay mahusay, hindi ba?
- Talaga?

384
00:18:41,333 --> 00:18:44,833
Oo. Hayaan mo akong linisin ito.
Bigyan mo ako ng kaunting kapayapaan, pakiusap.

385
00:18:44,833 --> 00:18:45,833
[Nag-spray]

386
00:18:45,833 --> 00:18:47,467
- Salamat, Cheska.
- Oo naman.

387
00:18:48,367 --> 00:18:51,300
- Justin lang ha?
- Oo, siya lang. pangako ko.

388
00:18:56,200 --> 00:18:58,533
- Oh, magandang laro, Martin!
- Magandang laro, Uncle.

389
00:18:58,600 --> 00:19:01,833
Galing talaga ni Gerard
ang kanyang pagiging mapagkumpitensya mula sa iyo.

390
00:19:03,033 --> 00:19:04,867
[MALAMANG NA MUSIC PLAYING]

391
00:19:04,867 --> 00:19:07,667
Well, I really wished
nakuha niya...

392
00:19:07,733 --> 00:19:09,900
ang instincts ko sa business.

393
00:19:09,900 --> 00:19:12,300
[TUMITIW]

394
00:19:12,300 --> 00:19:13,500
Ay...

395
00:19:13,633 --> 00:19:15,433
and speaking of business,

396
00:19:15,433 --> 00:19:17,733
[PATULOY ANG PLAYFUL MUSIC]

397
00:19:17,733 --> 00:19:19,333
Diretso ako sa punto.

398
00:19:21,100 --> 00:19:24,233
Mayroon akong mga reserbasyon
sa Hotel 88.

399
00:19:24,233 --> 00:19:27,533
Maaari nating pag-usapan ang mga tuntunin, Tiyo.
Kung yan ang gusto mo.

400
00:19:27,533 --> 00:19:32,467
[PATULOY ANG PLAYFUL MUSIC]

401
00:19:32,500 --> 00:19:34,300
- [PAG-SCRAP NG SINULO]
- Umupo.

402
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:41,867
salamat po.

403
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:46,033
Ang ganda ng proposal mo
sa papel.

404
00:19:47,267 --> 00:19:50,467
Pero alam ko rin kung ano
nangyari sa bookstore mo.

405
00:19:51,567 --> 00:19:54,900
Alam kong iba ang hotel
mula sa negosyong pinangasiwaan mo...

406
00:19:54,900 --> 00:19:57,367
kasama ang iyong ama, si Carlos.

407
00:19:58,833 --> 00:20:00,367
Kinausap ko siya.

408
00:20:03,467 --> 00:20:07,100
Paano ako makakasigurado na ito
hindi mangyayari sa investment ko?

409
00:20:07,100 --> 00:20:10,833
[Nagpe-play ng Penssive MUSIC]

410
00:20:10,833 --> 00:20:12,067
Aba...

411
00:20:13,267 --> 00:20:14,967
Oh, pupunta lang ako
para makuha ang menu.

412
00:20:14,967 --> 00:20:16,933
Hindi. Sari, okay lang.

413
00:20:16,933 --> 00:20:21,233
[MALAMANG NA MUSIC PLAYING]

414
00:20:23,600 --> 00:20:25,067
Ah, Tiyo...

415
00:20:26,267 --> 00:20:27,933
- [TRIXIE] Okay.
- [CHESKA] Hoy, hey, hey!

416
00:20:28,033 --> 00:20:30,567
Hoy, nagtatrabaho pa ako!
Hindi pa tapos ang shift ko!

417
00:20:30,700 --> 00:20:31,733
Ayan siya.

418
00:20:31,833 --> 00:20:33,100
Kausapin mo si Justin, bilisan mo.

419
00:20:33,267 --> 00:20:34,500
Sige na.

420
00:20:37,867 --> 00:20:38,700
[CHESKA] Kaibigan!

421
00:20:39,733 --> 00:20:40,500
Justin!

422
00:20:40,700 --> 00:20:42,133
Hoy, Justin, kaibigan ko!

423
00:20:42,233 --> 00:20:44,467
Anong balak mo?
Gustong tumambay?

424
00:20:44,633 --> 00:20:46,200
Busy ka ba sa negosyo mo?

425
00:20:46,333 --> 00:20:47,200
Baka next time.

426
00:20:47,333 --> 00:20:49,300
Kailangan ko lang makuha
ilang bagay dito.

427
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:51,000
Pupunta ka ba sa Kaluguran?

428
00:20:51,167 --> 00:20:52,167
Hindi.

429
00:20:52,333 --> 00:20:54,300
Ayoko lang dito.
Sinuspinde ako ng kapatid ko.

430
00:20:54,533 --> 00:20:57,500
Ano?! Bakit ka nasuspinde?
anong nangyari?

431
00:20:58,333 --> 00:20:59,467
Ay, wala.

432
00:20:59,900 --> 00:21:01,967
Message mo lang ako kung kailan
nasa Kaluguran ka.

433
00:21:02,133 --> 00:21:03,433
Doon tayo tumambay.

434
00:21:05,633 --> 00:21:06,967
Mag-ingat, aking kaibigan.

435
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:12,667
- [MELLOW MUSIC PLAYING]
- Oo? Oo, oo, oo?

436
00:21:12,867 --> 00:21:13,800
Nabigo.

437
00:21:15,033 --> 00:21:16,133
Wala siya sa mood.

438
00:21:18,033 --> 00:21:19,200
Diyos ko.

439
00:21:19,367 --> 00:21:20,500
[HINGA NG MAALALIM]

440
00:21:20,667 --> 00:21:22,067
ano ngayon?

441
00:21:23,600 --> 00:21:25,667
[MARTIN] Tiyo, alam mo
ang daming hotel

442
00:21:25,767 --> 00:21:27,833
mas kumikita kaysa sa
bookstores ngayon?

443
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:31,900
Araw-araw na cashflow, mas mataas na margin
sa peak season,

444
00:21:32,033 --> 00:21:36,200
at ang demand ay steady para sa
paglalakbay sa negosyo, at turismo.

445
00:21:36,367 --> 00:21:40,167
Lalo na sa Hotel 88, since
kilala ito sa lugar.

446
00:21:40,567 --> 00:21:41,700
Ano ang sinusubukan naming gawin

447
00:21:41,900 --> 00:21:45,367
ay nagsusulong para sa mas mataas na kita
potensyal para sa hotel.

448
00:21:45,900 --> 00:21:48,500
Dahil hindi lang ito ang
mga silid ng hotel na kumikita,

449
00:21:48,600 --> 00:21:50,767
may kita din
mula sa pagkain, mga kaganapan,

450
00:21:50,900 --> 00:21:53,067
at ang iba't ibang bakasyon
mga serbisyong inaalok namin.

451
00:21:53,767 --> 00:21:57,733
tama yan sir!
Tama si Sir Ice!

452
00:21:57,900 --> 00:21:59,167
Ibig kong sabihin, uh...

453
00:21:59,267 --> 00:22:01,733
...Tama si Martin.
Siya ay ganap na tama.

454
00:22:02,733 --> 00:22:06,033
Music festival ng hotel
katatapos lang,

455
00:22:06,133 --> 00:22:07,933
at ito ay isang malaking tagumpay.

456
00:22:08,067 --> 00:22:11,433
Maraming tao ang dumalo,
at kumuha ng mga kwarto sa hotel.

457
00:22:12,267 --> 00:22:13,767
"Ang iyong tagumpay?"

458
00:22:14,567 --> 00:22:16,267
Syempre, Uncle!

459
00:22:16,433 --> 00:22:18,733
Ang tagumpay niya ay tagumpay ko.

460
00:22:21,900 --> 00:22:23,433
Aba...

461
00:22:26,467 --> 00:22:28,067
Naghihintay ako ng sagot.

462
00:22:31,467 --> 00:22:33,200
Pag-iisipan ko
ang sinabi mo sa akin.

463
00:22:34,800 --> 00:22:37,767
Talagang inaabangan namin
sa pagtatrabaho sa iyo, Uncle.

464
00:22:39,800 --> 00:22:41,067
Umorder na tayo ng pagkain.

465
00:22:41,467 --> 00:22:42,633
Uh, waiter?

466
00:22:48,300 --> 00:22:49,767
Sari, huwag kang mahiya.

467
00:22:50,133 --> 00:22:51,300
Mag-order ng kahit anong gusto mo.

468
00:22:51,467 --> 00:22:52,633
salamat po.

469
00:22:53,633 --> 00:23:00,733
[UNEASY MUSIC PLAYING]

470
00:23:02,333 --> 00:23:03,233
[LINISIN ANG LUMAIN]

471
00:23:03,333 --> 00:23:06,967
[Tunog ng CELLPHONE]

472
00:23:07,133 --> 00:23:10,767
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

473
00:23:11,533 --> 00:23:12,933
Ano ang iyong nalaman?

474
00:23:14,133 --> 00:23:17,000
Nahanap ko ang kay Sandro Soliman
dating tirahan.

475
00:23:19,033 --> 00:23:20,933
Okay. Ipadala mo sa akin.

476
00:23:22,567 --> 00:23:23,800
Nagche-check out ako.

477
00:23:23,900 --> 00:23:24,967
[RECEPTIONIST] Okay, sir.

478
00:23:28,567 --> 00:23:35,633
[MUSIC CONTINUES]

479
00:23:40,133 --> 00:23:41,000
<i>Narito ang iyong kapatid?</i>

480
00:23:41,167 --> 00:23:42,833
<i>Isa ka bang lookout?
Nagtatrabaho ka sa kanya?</i>

481
00:23:42,900 --> 00:23:44,200
<i>Gusto mong malaman
kung nasaan ang iyong ama,</i>

482
00:23:44,333 --> 00:23:46,533
<i>at ano ang alam ng kapatid ko?
Tutulungan kita.</i>

483
00:23:46,667 --> 00:23:47,700
<i> Nasaan kayo ni Martin?</i>

484
00:23:47,800 --> 00:23:49,700
<i>Ang galaw mo para kausapin
Tiyo Ronald,</i>

485
00:23:49,833 --> 00:23:51,100
<i> iyon ay medyo palihim.</i>

486
00:23:51,200 --> 00:23:53,300
<i>Ito ang gagawin mo pagkatapos
ang aming "aktibidad sa pagbuo ng koponan?!"</i>

487
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:55,533
<i>- Anong pinagsasabi mo?!
- Nauna sila dito.</i>

488
00:23:55,700 --> 00:23:57,033
<i> Lumalaban lang ako.</i>

489
00:23:57,200 --> 00:23:59,333
<i>Wala kang nagawa
ngunit humarang ka sa amin!</i>

490
00:23:59,433 --> 00:24:02,367
Bakit hindi mo subukang intindihin
<i> ano ang sinusubukan kong makamit?!</i>

491
00:24:02,533 --> 00:24:04,467
<i>Sinisikap ko lang
protektahan ang aking pamilya!</i>

492
00:24:04,567 --> 00:24:06,833
<i>At sinusubukan ko
protektahan ang hotel!</i>

